26 Dec 2013 21:53






He absorbed the power that's released when a reality bender (here 1915) creates something. Since something is created from nothing, an opposite force (unmaking) also comes into being. Usually it's just released to harmful effects, but 1915 made sure it was safely stored for the narrator to find. When he absorved the power, however, he realized he couldn't use it for good, hence his ultimate conclusion to unmake himself.







